io.github.splotycode.mosaik.gameengine.gameloop

Class TickFrameLoop

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.splotycode.mosaik.gameengine.gameloop.TickFrameLoop
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GameLoop, Overloadable

    public class TickFrameLoop
extends java.lang.Object
implements GameLoop, Overloadable
    This Game Loop while call Ticks at a consistent rate It will try to catch up with tick if it is behind (up to 20 ticks) It has as many render cycles as it can or as the fpsCap allows
